data.description: Quiet simple living in this 3 bedroom 1 bath ranch/bungalow home with large fenced in back yard and detached garage.  Upstairs is considered to be the third bedroom; however, it is large enough to be a possible fourth bedroom as well or large bonus area.  Roof was replaced in 2022.  Full unfinished basement with laundry hookups, as well as plumbing for an additional bath if desired.  Please add this to your list of homes to tour privately with your realtor.
